text: Located at 8th floor (top floor), this canteen serves basic delicacies ranging from Chinese to Indian, as well as Thai. Total 6 food stalls (currently only 5 operating), as well as a drink stall. A convenient place for ppl working within this building, price wise a bit on the high side, and choice wise average only. Can't be choosy since the location does not require you to walk far.
Tahiti isnt an ordinary coffee shop, it is far from that. The food tastes amazing the vibes are extremely chill. I highly suggest visiting!
Tahiti is not just ordinary coffee, it is extraordinary, creates a cool vibe with a very relaxed atmosphere, and is very much the best coffee I have ever tried, let alone the rich toast.
Verryy good placee! The food taste amazingg!! It was a revelation ,surpassing anything found in the typical kopitiam setting!!
